item.title: Ep. 194 – Trendsetter Talkback
item.description:
It’s Daddy’s last episode on the couch for a couple of weeks so we cover the real problems of the world, including rusty trombones, banana’s in the doot and some classic marketplace yarns. A few crack ups with some gratitude content sprinkled through to end the episode on a high note. Enjoy legends!


Got a yarn? Send an mp3 voice recording as an email to carryon@alphablokes.com.au
